room_title: Escape room "The Candy Shop" by Expedition Escape in Montgomeryville
review: This is the third escape room I've done so far, and so far the best! We did the Candy Shop and had so much fun, the employee that helped us was super helpful fun and nice. Will definitely come back to do more!

room_title: Escape room "The Candy Shop" by Expedition Escape in Montgomeryville
review: I've done about 10 escape rooms and this place is by far the best I've been to! The rooms all have amazing props and puzzles. We did the Candy Shop tonight and you really feel like you're in a candy shop! Great job Expedition Escape! I'll definitely be returning!
